    narr:narration """This hub tracks recurring linguistic signatures that define the speaker's rhetorical style. The primary anchor remains the [narrative source of truth](narr:StyleObs_StockPhrase_1), a concept frequently paired with the more concise [source of truth](narr:StyleObs_stock_phrase_source_of_truth) to establish foundational authority. These are complemented by business-centric idioms that delineate power dynamics and methodology, specifically identifying [who signs the checks](narr:StyleObs_StockPhrase_SignsChecks) to locate economic decision-making and utilizing [train the trainers](narr:StyleObs_TrainTrainers) to frame consulting engagements. The collection also captures process-oriented shorthand, such as the informal [kick the tires](narr:StyleObs_2) for validation, and the cautionary [state secrets to AI](narr:StyleObs_StockPhrase_StateSecrets), which serves as a recurring metaphor for the risks inherent in entrusting proprietary context to external models. These phrases function as stable semantic markers, anchoring complex organizational and technical arguments within a consistent, recognizable voice.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_2> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_StockPhrase_1> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_StockPhrase_SignsChecks> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_StockPhrase_StateSecrets> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_TrainTrainers> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_stock_phrase_source_of_truth> ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "narrative source of truth" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_StockPhrase_1> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "source of truth" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_stock_phrase_source_of_truth> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "who's really the guy who signs the checks" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_StockPhrase_SignsChecks> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "let me train the trainers and let me bring every thinking" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_TrainTrainers> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "when you tell state secrets to AI, you depend on that AI's memory" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_StockPhrase_StateSecrets> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "kick the tires" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_2> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The phrase 'kick the tires' is framed as an informal, process-oriented validation, contrasting with the more rigid, authoritative tone of the 'source of truth' anchors." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_2> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_StockPhrase_1> ] ;
